alth","Health","2016-02-04","Mental Health Services","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Health, what proportion of the funding for Improving Access to Psychological Therapies services since 2010 has been spent on training and development of people working in such services.","false","Biography information for Luciana Berger","Liverpool, Wavertree","Luciana Berger","25996"
